# Daily Circular Planner

Interactive 24-hour circular planner with a weekly schedule view. Built with Next.js, React, Tailwind CSS, and Radix UI components.

- Main UI: [`CircularPlanner`](app/page.tsx)
- Utility: [`cn`](lib/utils.ts)
- Toasts: [`Toaster`](components/ui/toaster.tsx), [`useToast`](hooks/use-toast.ts)

## Features

- Drag-and-drop tasks onto a 24-hour circular timetable
- Weekly view with day columns and quick navigation (Previous, Today, Next)
- Snap-to-minute granularity (5/15/30/60)
- Conflict detection, undo/redo history
- Export/Import JSON
- Dark mode
- Category-based time statistics

## Tech

- Next.js 16 ([package.json](package.json), [next.config.mjs](next.config.mjs))
- React 19
- Tailwind CSS v4 ([app/globals.css](app/globals.css), [styles/globals.css](styles/globals.css))
- Radix UI + shadcn components ([components.json](components.json))
- Icons: lucide-react

## Getting started

```sh
# Install
pnpm install

# Development
pnpm dev

# Build
pnpm build

# Start (production)
pnpm start
```

Node 18+ recommended.

## Project structure

- App shell: [app/layout.tsx](app/layout.tsx)
- Planner UI: [app/page.tsx](app/page.tsx) as [`CircularPlanner`](app/page.tsx)
- UI primitives: [components/ui](components/ui)
- Utilities: [lib/utils.ts](lib/utils.ts) as [`cn`](lib/utils.ts)
- Toast system: [components/ui/toaster.tsx](components/ui/toaster.tsx), [hooks/use-toast.ts](hooks/use-toast.ts)

## Usage

- Daily view: drag tasks from the left list onto the circle. Resize by dragging handles; snapping is configurable.
- Weekly view: add/edit/remove tasks per day; navigate week with header controls.
- History: use Undo/Redo in the task sidebar.
- Export/Import: JSON controls in the sidebar.
- Stats: toggle Stats in the header; view per-category totals.
- Dark mode: toggle in the header.

## Notes

- Client state persists via localStorage (arcs, tasks, weekly tasks, preferences).
- Images are unoptimized by config ([next.config.mjs](next.config.mjs)).

